        "Njan Njan": "Njan njan njan njan vythyasthanaam<br/>Nee nee nee nee Vyathyasthanam(2)<br/>Nammalellam vyathyastharaa(2)<br/>Aananthathode aamodhathode paadaam hooi..<br/><br/>Jumna jumna jumnaa na hoi (2)<br/><br/>Enne pole ee bhoovil<br/>Vere aarum illallo<br/>Ninne pole ee bhoovil<br/>Vere aarum illallo<br/>Ente roopam pole<br/>Ente kannukal pole<br/>Ente punchiri pole <br/>Ente nadatham pole<br/>Ee bhoovil veraarum illallo<br/>Ee bhoovil veraarum illallo<br/><br/>Njan thikachum vyathyasthanaa<br/>Daivam thanna sammanamaa(2)<br/>Aananthathode aamodhathode paadaam hooi..<br/><br/>Jumna jumna jumnaa na hoi (2)<br/><br/>",
