        "Tring Tring Tring": "Tring tring tring cycle gadi<br/>Pom pom pom motor gadi<br/>Hurrah bheil gadi<br/>Hurrah bheil gadi<br/>Alleiliah Alleiliah <br/>Yesu chalata hai jeevan ki gadi <br/>Yesu chalata hai jeevan ki gadi <br/><br/>Konsi gadi chal rahi hein Bhayoon <br/>Konsi gadi chal rahi hein Bhehanoon<br/><br/>Yesu Sathya hein<br/>Yesu marg hein<br/>Yesu chalata hai jeevan ki gadi<br/>Yesu chalata hai jeevan ki gadi<br/><br/>",
        "Unda Kannulla": "Unda kannulla sathane<br/>Ninneyenikku vendaalo<br/>Sundaranaamen yeshuvullappol<br/>Ninneyenukku vendaalo<br/><br/>Purakil vaalulla sathane<br/>Ninneyenikku vendaalo<br/>Sundaranaamen yeshuvullappol<br/>Ninneyenukku vendaalo<br/><br/>",
        "Watermelon": "Watermelon Watermelon<br/>Pinepple pineapple<br/>Bananananaana Bananananaana<br/>Fruitsalaad Fruitsalaad<br/><br/>God the Father God the Father<br/>God the Son God the Son<br/>God the Holy Spirit <br/>God the Holy Spirit <br/>Three in one Three in one<br/><br/>",
