        "When You're Jumping": "When you're jumping, <br/>Jumping up and down<br/>When you're spinning, <br/>Spinning round and round<br/>God's seeing everything you do<br/>He's watching, watching over you<br/><br/>Hey<br/>God is watching, watching over you,<br/>24/7 watching over you<br/>Your life is in His hands ooh ooh <br/>He's got great big plans <br/>Cos He's watching over you<br/><br/>When you're waving, <br/>Your hands up in the air<br/>When you're shouting, <br/>No matter when or where<br/>God's seeing everything you do<br/>He's watching, watching over you<br/><br/>God is watching, watching over you,<br/>24/7 watching over you<br/>Your life is in His hands ooh<br/>He's got great big plans <br/>Cos He's watching over you<br/><br/>",
