        "You Have Turned": "<em>Your light broke through my night<br/>Restored exceeding joy<br/>Your grace fell like the rain<br/>And made this desert live<br/><br/>You have turned my mourning into dancing<br/>You have turned my sorrow into joy<br/><br/>Your hand lifted me up<br/>I stand on higher ground<br/>Your praise rose in my heart<br/>And made this valley sing</em><br/><br/>You have turned my mourning into dancing<br/>You have turned my sorrow into joy<br/>You have turned my mourning into dancing<br/>You have turned my sorrow into joy<br/><br/>This is how we overcome<br/>This is how we overcome<br/><br/>This is how we overcome<br/>This is how we overcome<br/>This is how we overcome<br/>This is how we over<br/><br/>You have turned my mourning into dancing<br/>You have turned my sorrow into joy<br/>You have turned my mourning into dancing<br/>You have turned my sorrow into joy<br/><br/>",
        "Aajaa Mere": "Aajaa Mere Prabhu<br/>Aajaa mere prabhu<br/>Mere dil mein, mere tann mein<br/>Aaajaa prabhu<br/><br/>Tu aakar mujhko change kar de<br/>Mere hriday ko saaf kar de<br/>Tu hi prabhu muktidaata<br/>Tu hi prabhu muktidaata<br/>Mujh par daya karo<br/><br/>Paapon se main balheen hua<br/>Tujh se bahut main door hua<br/>Mere prabhu mere swami<br/>Mere prabhu mere swami<br/>Mujh par daya karo<br/><br/>Vachnon se meri pyaas bujhaa<br/>Tere ishaaron pe chalna sikha<br/>Tu hai prabhu jeevan ka bal<br/>Tu hai prabhu jeevan ka bal<br/>Mujh par daya karo<br/><br/>",
        "Stuti Aradhana": "Stuthi aradhana upar jati hai<br/>Ashishe dekho neeche aati hai<br/><br/>Mera iswar kitna mahaan<br/>Dekho hamse karta hai pyar<br/><br/>Hallelu halleluiyah<br/><br/>Hallelu halleluiyah<br/><br/>Prarthna vinti upar jati hai,<br/>Uttar lekar neeche aati hai<br/>Prabhu hamara kitna mahan<br/>Dekho hamse karta hai pyar<br/>Hallelu halleluiyah<br/>Hallelu halleluiyah<br/><br/>",
        "Tere Paas": "Tere paas ata hu,<br/>Yeshu tere paas <br/><br/>Tere paas aata hu,<br/>Yeshu tere paas <br/><br/>Her pal meri her saans,<br/>Teri mahi ma gaati rahe<br/>Her din meri her baat,<br/>Teri stuti kerti rahe<br/><br/>Yeshu aa <br/><br/>",
